               stealing three linen shirts, value 30 s. a linen shift, value 5 s. a callico jacket, value 5 s. a bed-gown, value 10 s. a linen petticoat, value 5 s. two linen pillow cases, value 2 s. and a linen night-cap, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17780115-21-victim246" type="victimName">
